data.description: Welcome home to 113 Woodland Heights!  A spacious foyer sets a welcoming tone as you enter the house. Inside, you have 4 bedrooms and 3.5 bathrooms, which provide plenty of living space and convenience. The gourmet kitchen is perfect for cooking and entertaining. The master suite, with its spa-like bathroom, serves as a private retreat within the home. The additional three bedrooms upstairs offer plenty of space, with two of them featuring Jack and Jill bathrooms, which is convenient for shared use. Outside you will find a large deck for relaxation and gatherings which includes an outdoor kitchen, and a 7 X 15 spa perfect for entertaining friends and family. You will also find a 25 X 42 garage/storage/workshop building. Overall, it is a beautiful and well-equipped residence that offers both comfort and style.
